The '''Dead Explorer''' is located at the entrance to the [[Stronghold of Security]]. This is the skeleton of [[Solztun]] who is located at the end of the dungeon, and will imbue the players [[Skull sceptre]] if they have [[authenticator]] enabled on their account. Searching the remains will give the player a dialogue box saying "You rummage around in the dead explorer's bag....." and gives the player the [[Stronghold notes]]. If the player already has a copy of the book and tries to search the remains it will say "You don't find anything."
